OL,3,CDrug shortages 'heaping pressure' on
OL,4,Calready stretched pharmacies
OL,6,FA jump in the number of alerts issued
OL,7,Fto warn pharmacists that certain drugs
OL,8,Fare in short supply is "just the tip
OL,9,Fof the iceberg" when it comes to the
OL,10,Fchallenges the sector is facing,
OL,11,Fexperts have warned.
OL,13,FThe unpredictability of the issue is
OL,14,Falso a "huge source of worry" for
OL,15,Fpatients, they said.
