OL,3,CDrug shortages 'heaping pressure' on
OL,4,Calready stretched pharmacies
OL,6,FIt comes as analysis by the National
OL,7,FPharmacy Association (NPA) found the
OL,8,Fnumber of Serious Shortage Protocols
OL,9,F(SSPs) ` alerts that notify pharmacies
OL,10,Fthat they may need to supply an
OL,11,Falternative medication to patients `
OL,12,Fhas gone up by three and a half times
OL,13,Fin the last two years.
OL,15,FThe organisation has called for
OL,16,Fpolitical parties to commit to
OL,17,Ftackling the "crisis" in the sector in
OL,18,Fthe run up to the General Election.
OL,26,@yD@NOUyD@UO]
