OL,6,FHave you heard our new podcast Talking
OL,7,FPolitics? Every week Tom, Robert and
OL,8,FAnushka dig into the biggest issues
OL,9,Fdominating the political agenda...
OL,11,FAccording to the NPA, there have been
OL,12,F50 SSPs issued by the Department of
OL,13,FHealth and Social Care between 2022
OL,14,Fand 2024 compared to 15 between 2019
OL,15,Fand 2021.
OL,17,FThe analysis found the alerts were for
OL,18,Fa range of conditions, including
OL,19,Fepilepsy, angina, menopause, thyroid
OL,20,Fproblems and depression.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G3/14
