OL,6,FFour SSPs were sent out over a three-
OL,7,Fday period in May alone, the NPA
OL,8,Fclaims, the same number that have been
OL,9,Fissued for the whole of 2020.
OL,11,FPaul Rees, chief executive of the NPA,
OL,12,Fsaid: "The national warnings are only
OL,13,Fissued when shortages are at their
OL,14,Fmost acute, with this revealing just
OL,15,Fthe tip of the iceberg, in terms of
OL,16,Fthe challenges facing pharmacies and
OL,17,Ftheir patients.
OL,26,@tD@GOU
