OL,3,CDrug shortages 'heaping pressure' on
OL,4,Calready stretched pharmacies
OL,6,F"Pharmacists will always help patients
OL,7,Fget alternative medication, when
OL,8,Fpossible, but they face continual
OL,9,Fstruggles obtaining supply across an
OL,10,Fever-changing range of conditions,
OL,11,Ffrom diabetes to ADHD and epilepsy.
OL,13,F"Pharmacists are spending hours a day
OL,14,Fhunting down stock and are often
OL,15,Fforced to turn patients away due to
OL,16,Fbeing unable to order in vital
OL,17,Fmedication."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUyD@LO]
