OL,6,FRebekah Smith, deputy chief executive
OL,7,Fof the charity Epilepsy Action, added:
OL,8,F"It's extremely concerning to see the
OL,9,Fimpact medication shortages are having
OL,10,Fon people with epilepsy, and that the
OL,11,Fissue still hasn't been resolved.
OL,13,F"The journey to finding the right
OL,14,Fmedication, or the right combination,
OL,15,Fcan be tough for people with epilepsy.
OL,16,FBut when they do find it, they
OL,17,Fshouldn't have to fear losing the
OL,18,Fsecurity it gives."
OL,26,@pD@AOUuD@AOUzD@SO]
