OL,6,FMs Smith said calls to the Epilepsy
OL,7,FAction helpline regarding concerns
OL,8,Fabout medication shortages have
OL,9,Fincreased four-fold since the start of
OL,10,Fthe year.
OL,12,F"It goes without saying that the
OL,13,Funpredictability of the issue has been
OL,14,Fa huge source of worry," she added.
OL,16,F"Not getting the right medication
OL,17,Fcould mean more seizures, or even
OL,18,Fhaving one after being seizure-free
OL,19,Ffor years.
OL,26,@tD@AOUvD@XO]xD@AOU
