OL,6,F"This could have a massive knock-on
OL,7,Feffect to many aspects of a person's
OL,8,Flife, such as their ability to drive,
OL,9,For their job. It can cause side-
OL,10,Feffects.
OL,12,F"At its worst, it can be life-
OL,13,Fthreatening. People with epilepsy
OL,14,Fdon't deserve to have to go through
OL,15,Fthis."
