OL,3,CDrug shortages 'heaping pressure' on
OL,4,Calready stretched pharmacies
OL,6,FMenopause specialist and GP Dr Louise
OL,7,FNewson described the shortage of
OL,8,Fhormone replacement therapy (HRT) for
OL,9,Fmenopause as "a public health
OL,10,Fcatastrophe", adding that "women
OL,11,Fdeserve better".
OL,13,FShe said shortages have been caused by
OL,14,Fincreased demand, with women now more
OL,15,Faware of the benefits of HRT, which
OL,16,Frelieves menopausal symptoms.
OL,18,F"HRT shortages have had a detrimental
OL,19,Feffect on women seeking HRT, GP
OL,20,Fsurgeries and also pharmacists," Dr
OL,21,FNewson said.
OL,26,@qD@NOUrD@LO]rD@[OUsD@OO]zD@AOU|D@`O]
