OL,6,F"There are risks to future health of
OL,7,Fnot having HRT as well as more
OL,8,Fimmediate effects of symptoms
OL,9,Foccurring, including low mood, poor
OL,10,Fsleep, anxiety, headaches, urine
OL,11,Finfections and joint pains, without
OL,12,Fhormones."
OL,14,FIt comes after MPs urged the
OL,15,Fgovernment to "get a grip" on drugs
OL,16,Fshortages and commission an
OL,17,Findependent review of the medicines
OL,18,Fsupply chain.
