OL,6,FThe Health and Social Care Committee
OL,7,Fsaid the issue is leaving Pharmacy
OL,8,FFirst, which launched in January, at
OL,9,Frisk of failure.
OL,11,FThe policy allows patients to be
OL,12,Ftreated for seven common conditions at
OL,13,Ftheir local pharmacy without the need
OL,14,Ffor a GP appointment or prescription.
OL,16,FBut MPs warned that patients could be
OL,17,Freluctant to visit pharmacies for
OL,18,Fclinical services if medication is out
OL,19,Fof stock, and said Pharmacy First will
OL,20,F"fail if people keep having to return
OL,21,Fto their GP".
