OL,6,FThe report by the Health and Social
OL,7,FCare Committee, published as part of
OL,8,Fits inquiry into pharmacy services,
OL,9,Falso called for a "complete overhaul"
OL,10,Fof the funding framework for community
OL,11,Fpharmacy if the sector is to realise
OL,12,Fits potential.
OL,14,FMr Rees added: "It's clear that these
OL,15,Fgrowing medicine shortages are heaping
OL,16,Fpressure on our already stretched
OL,17,Flocal community pharmacy teams.
OL,26,@qD@SOUqD@eO]vD@POU
