OL,6,F"The current funding crisis ` which
OL,7,Fhas seen support for pharmacies fall
OL,8,Fby 40% over the last decade in real
OL,9,Fterms ` is a key issue in driving
OL,10,Fthese appalling shortages.
OL,12,F"It is imperative that all the main
OL,13,Fparties commit during the General
OL,14,FElection campaign to addressing the
OL,15,Fcrisis facing community pharmacy `
OL,16,Fwhich is a key factor in the medicines
OL,17,Fshortages.
